{"tid":95123,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"免費叫雞 受賄款  反黑警司被捕","createTime":"2017-01-25T19:21:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-26T06:26:15.000Z","uid":62257,"like":73,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8328fed3d71140c952500b0df20963ac897ef2ee","tid":95123,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T19:21:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170126/56224317\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170126%2F56224317&d=ZH4yc4t%2FNb3Zc6B%2FQrMq52N6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=d389dd1a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170126%2F56224317&h=7aa1ef64\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170126/56224317</a><br />\n<br />\n廉署前日出動逾百人展開大規模行動，拘捕12名男女，當中包括3名警務人員，他們分別是港島總區刑事總部警司吳偉漢、有組織罪案及三合會調查科（俗稱「O記」）高級督察陳嘉健和港島總區反黑組探員鍾文浩，當中有人涉嫌收受黑幫賄款及獲安排免費嫖妓，作為協助申請酒牌、查閱警方機密資料、包庇及通風報訊的報酬。其餘9名被捕者包括吳偉漢妻子及灣仔兩家夜總會的經營者和職員。<br />\n<br />\n記者：劉漢權 胡恩宏<br />\n<br />\n被捕警司吳偉漢、高級督察陳嘉健（28歲）及警員鍾文浩（32歲），目前仍被廉署扣查。據了解，吳偉漢長期駐守刑偵部門，曾駐守油尖旺警區刑事偵緝部、有組織罪案及三合會調查科及港島總區刑事總部。上月8日，他剛召開記者會交代警方卧底行動，掃蕩黑幫淫窟及地下賭場。<br />\n<br />\n吳妻涉助運款北上被拘<br />\n<br />\n吳偉漢前年年底調往港島總區刑事總部，之前隸屬O記，當時陳嘉健及鍾文浩為其下屬。消息稱，由於他主管的調查工作，主要針對黑幫犯罪活動，因工作關係，與黑幫高層有接觸，亦因此成為黑幫收買目標。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，吳偉漢前晚在外與人見面後，被跟蹤的廉署人員截停，當場在他身上搜出十多萬元現金。其後，廉署人員在多處地點行動，包括在兩個住宅地址拘捕陳嘉健和鍾文浩，以及在灣仔兩家夜總會拘捕兩名老闆及三名職員，另外再拘捕四名男女，其中一名女子是吳妻。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，吳過往多次收取賄款，並將數十萬元的現金交由妻子帶回內地收藏。廉署人員之後搜查3警位於港島總部及O記的辦公室、住所和夜總會等，並撿走一批證物。<br />\n<br />\n被指查警機密通風報信<br />\n<br />\n廉署表示，早前接獲貪污投訴後展開調查，發現案中的警務人員涉嫌收受夜總會經營者及相關人士提供巨額現金賄款及其他形式利益，作為向他們預先提供警方行動消息、協助申請酒牌或濫用其未獲授權查閱的資料的報酬。另有消息稱，被捕3警中，除有人收賄款外，更享受免費嫖妓等款待。<br />\n<br />\n警方發言人表示，案件調查期間，警方一直積極配合廉政公署的工作。警隊一直非常重視警務人員的誠信及品格，內部透過誠信管理策略加強人員相關操守。警隊對於犯罪及違規行為一直採取零容忍態度。<br />\n<br />\n對上一次廉署拘捕警司級人員已是於5年前，廉署以涉嫌公職人員行為失當罪拘控灣仔分區指揮官黃冠豪，黃被指先後多次光顧一間食肆，獲提供折扣優惠及送贈威士忌，換取他審閱食肆酒牌申請時不作反對，2013年6月被裁定罪成，被判監12個月。<br />\n<br />\n此外，高級警司冼錦華，2001年在隸屬O記期間，獲夜總會老闆林春葉多次安排享免費貴價晚宴，之後再派女公關到酒店為冼提供免費性服務，甚至玩一皇兩后，以換取冼在林經營的夜總會及酒吧「通水」，2003年被裁定三項公職人員行為失當罪成，入獄3年，上訴後獲改判2年。"},{"pid":"5b2281597dc6f01244d6643b648d9d57b2fe65bc","tid":95123,"uid":37030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T19:36:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c378610a24bec63d80619ca80992f851fea22fb7","tid":95123,"uid":55077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T19:58:38.000Z","msg":"咁仲算係小錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bb55943458d9ff796db212881f87ced5fc05a7f","tid":95123,"uid":408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T20:00:35.000Z","msg":"據悉，吳偉漢前晚在外與人見面後，被跟蹤的廉署人員截停，當場在他身上搜出十多萬元現金。其後，廉署人員在多處地點行動，包括在兩個住宅地址拘捕陳嘉健和鍾文浩，以及在灣仔兩家夜總會拘捕兩名老闆及三名職員，另外再拘捕四名男女，其中一名女子是吳妻。<br />\n<br />\n當場斷正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d812ffbf2b39fe69bf6c98e8130ed21261fc20a8","tid":95123,"uid":29784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T20:01:51.000Z","msg":"比人篤架啦"},{"pid":"dfa882a3c4706bab1beb717a8c89c7f6307281c8","tid":95123,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T20:04:41.000Z","msg":"叫雞唔使比錢既黑警<br />\n但唔使比錢咁算唔算嫖"},{"pid":"e5c9798857c3957a9bcb664001dbb9dfa7f23171","tid":95123,"uid":1085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T20:10:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"639879b0c39c1aebd520a7bed0aa19e130aefde6","tid":95123,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T20:21:00.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">原來吳聖人2個月前先至老來得子，俗語有話差人愛邪牌，大家又估下佢老婆係咪蝗族呢可？？？有冇驗DNA咁呢？？？</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/26/010442_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F26%2F010442_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=a027e16b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170125/photo/bkn-20170125215842764-0125_00822_001_01p.jpg?20170125233803\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170125%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170125215842764-0125_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20170125233803&h=bd7f06a4&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n被廉署拘捕另外2名警務人員，其中高級督察陳嘉健為港大尖子，被視為警隊「明日之星」，另一名反黑探員鍾文浩曾是臥底黑幫的「無間道」，去年獲盧偉聰頒發處長嘉許狀。陳和鍾同樣都有反黑經驗及與「O記」有交集。<br />\n<br />\n年僅28歲的陳，被捕前駐守有組織罪案及三合會調查科，他2012年曾接受傳媒訪問，親述投考警隊的經歷，表明身為督察須有熱誠，認為即使面對困難亦不能退縮，且要有承擔去完成每一個任務。<br />\n<br />\n陳嘉健2010年畢業於香港大學工程系，大學二年級時參加警隊學長計劃後，立志加入警隊。他後來透過「警務督察招募快線」投考督察，畢業前已通過警隊考核程序，並在畢業後隨即接受警察學院36周的訓練，先擔任軍裝巡邏小隊指揮官，再轉往旺角警區刑事調查隊，曾駐守旺角警區反黑組，其後調任有組織罪案及三合會調查科。<br />\n<br />\n33歲的偵緝警員鍾文浩，2010年11月獲「O記」招攬，滲入黑幫作臥底搜證，協助偵破屯門黑幫「新X安」一宗廝殺案，案中綽號「郭靖」的18歲青年被人用刀襲擊及用汽車輾過死亡，警方其後拘捕疑兇。鍾文浩於2014年6月，以臥底警員身份上庭作供。2016年6月23日，鍾獲警務處處長盧偉聰頒予嘉許狀。</blockquote><br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/25/233905_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F25%2F233905_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=32e28bc4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/25/233932_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F25%2F233932_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=ff2cf913&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/25/233951_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F25%2F233951_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=6c125857&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/25/234001_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F25%2F234001_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=e099270c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/25/234015_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F25%2F234015_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=5487b47b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/25/234026_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F25%2F234026_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=8c6ed135&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/25/234040_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F25%2F234040_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=e1fbaed6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/26/000623_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F26%2F000623_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=15f6a296&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/26/001642_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F26%2F001642_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=a7be1cb3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"760d85341c93a46994eeff043e825398db940d0b","tid":95123,"uid":71315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T20:30:34.000Z","msg":"今年 28 歲，15 年做過署任總督察，即係高級督察，26 歲就高級督察，人生贏家 ..."},{"pid":"414bbae97c2e84dad0bf51eab767ac76bd8b9b60","tid":95123,"uid":71655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T20:57:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f211d737f86a5a892e95bbdd8f164886986a5dd5","tid":95123,"uid":23141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T21:13:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今年 28 歲，15 年做過署任總督察，即係高級督察，26 歲就高級督察，人生贏家 ...</blockquote><br />\n今次唔方唔人生贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4b313c494671af46876ee97b4590716591b8fc5","tid":95123,"uid":1096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T22:23:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無人通水。邊有咁多大案破</blockquote><br />\n味係，老廉蠢過閪呀，睇吓今次又會唔會程序出錯放犯"},{"pid":"4009ab0b4ea2e53034a836d3b11b87c1c22433fd","tid":95123,"uid":16343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T22:27:26.000Z","msg":"個高級督察咁就玩完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d2db097b66898d3db7096b8034b431e39b3e34b","tid":95123,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T23:48:34.000Z","msg":"好福利<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35f0f08cfc6181d1818444343a8484220ff25142","tid":95123,"uid":42044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T23:53:51.000Z","msg":"廉署攞分數啫，為左俾外國人睇香港仲係好廉。暗地裡 d黑警會冇事，或者件案拖到黑警退休，又變成一個朱經偉。"},{"pid":"4c5c90be52626fbe80c0a45574e89a1eb97eef1c","tid":95123,"uid":28619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T23:55:31.000Z","msg":"極醜惡系列"},{"pid":"978b20866a223b6d7a3e2ccd6b5219d57d5eb4b1","tid":95123,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T23:56:23.000Z","msg":"聖人系列<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ec718321fdec2d1cf90ddc53fc29c286f2d63c9","tid":95123,"uid":29080,"li