\"><span style=\"color: red;\">釘姐歡喜哥溶左未？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"47a0fbff7d6e1f763959b381bc28e8c1743557bd","tid":95123,"uid":57488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T04:58:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你個高級督察大學打波時識 細我一屆<br />\n人地已經搵咁多錢 黑白兩道玩哂 仲有得叫免費雞<br />\n<br />\n相反自己仲成碌7咁</blockquote><br />\n佢邊科Eng畢業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d706bc34aca851f9ba1a9dcb977c69e8e659c449","tid":95123,"uid":66189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T05:01:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>屌你個高級督察大學打波時識 細我一屆<br />\n人地已經搵咁多錢 黑白兩道玩哂 仲有得叫免費雞<br />\n<br />\n相反自己仲成碌7咁</blockquote><br />\n佢邊科Eng畢業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n工業工程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n抵死<br />\n掛住住hall唔做野得個樣既free rider"},{"pid":"524d1a2e23df5dc507b13496d8eb0d42f62cd1a0","tid":95123,"uid":57488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T05:16:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>屌你個高級督察大學打波時識 細我一屆<br />\n人地已經搵咁多錢 黑白兩道玩哂 仲有得叫免費雞<br />\n<br />\n相反自己仲成碌7咁</blockquote><br />\n佢邊科Eng畢業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n工業工程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n抵死<br />\n掛住住hall唔做野得個樣既free rider</blockquote><br />\n佢就位啦<br />\n我諗同屆嘅冇乜邊個有哩個人工<br />\n咁都要貪真係抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed37c4b15556b86f2c66d8b961677eb7bf891329","tid":95123,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T05:18:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>屌你個高級督察大學打波時識 細我一屆<br />\n人地已經搵咁多錢 黑白兩道玩哂 仲有得叫免費雞<br />\n<br />\n相反自己仲成碌7咁</blockquote><br />\n佢邊科Eng畢業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br